Subject: [PATCH] fix(contact-landlord): clean corrupted UTF-8, add logo to nav

- Remove mojibake + stray C1 control bytes (Windows-1252/UTF-8 corruption) from
  comment banners and the user-facing em-dash fallbacks shown when a property
  can't be loaded; fallbacks now display a clean em-dash.
- Add the FindMyNyumba logo to the nav (img with graceful text fallback,
  matching browse.html) in place of the plain text brand link.
- Keep cover_url-first thumbnail logic from the media upgrade.
logo.png already existed in the repo and is unchanged.
